atre affich\u00e9 dans les premiers r\u00e9sultats de recherche de Google et d\u2019augmenter vos ventes ainsi que votre chiffre d\u2019affaires. D\u00e9couvrons ensemble les sp\u00e9cificit\u00e9s des campagnes Google Shopping ainsi que les optimisations possibles pour des campagnes r\u00e9ussies !<\/p>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row my=&#8221;2&#8243;][vc_column]<div class=\"image-single-wrapper visuel-article text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/google-shopping.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"google shopping\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/google-shopping.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/google-shopping-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/google-shopping-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/google-shopping-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row my=&#8221;2&#8243;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V